title: Three IAF commando groups air-dropped to find suspected Pakistanis in Sir Creek area, operation underway - Times Now
content: Three IAF commando groups air-dropped to find suspected Pakistanis in Sir Creek area, operation underway  Times Now
description: The BSF, earlier in the day, informed that eleven Pakistani fishing boats have been seized in the creek area of Harami Nalla in Gujarat's Bhuj.
